We will work in the directory /home/cloudera/train/oozie  on the local node for oozie exercises.

oozie workflows need to be stored on HDFS. So create a HDFS directory called /user/cloudera/workflows to store the oozie workflows

We will creating the following oozie workflows.

1. Oozie workflow to create a directory on HDFS

2. Oozie worklfow using hive2 action to insert data into a hive table.

3. Oozie workflow using sqoop action to sqoop data into HDFS
